The dissertation is available in two formats.
  • Original format, as submitted to the University.
    • gzipped Postscript (430K)
    • Acrobat PDF (1.25M).
  • Single-spaced format, without the copyright, dedication, acknowledgements, my CV, table of contents, and lists of figures and tables.
    • gzipped Postscript (415K)
    • Acrobat PDF (1.15M).
